      "note_no": "92",
      "note": "Regarding the Qur'anic concept of \"intercession\" on the Day of Judgment, see note 7 on 10:3. The \"word [of faith]\" referred to towards the end of the above verse is - according to Ibn 'Abbas (as quoted by Baghawi) - a metonym for the belief that \"there is no deity save God\", i.e., the realization of His oneness and uniqueness. See also 19:87 and the corresponding note 74."
